                "description_de": "Die Anwendung verwendet fehlerhafte XSS-Filter, die durch alternative Kodierungen, Manipulation von Tag-Attributen oder nicht-rekursives Filtern (z. B. <scr<script>ipt>) umgangen werden k\u00f6nnen.",
                "consequences_en": "Attackers can circumvent existing security controls (like WAFs or input sanitizers) to successfully execute Cross-Site Scripting attacks.",
